# Format Check Guardrail

After editing any file under `frontend/`, verify formatting before finishing the task:

```bash
cd frontend && npm run format:check
```

If it fails, auto-fix and re-check:

```bash
cd frontend && npm run format && npm run format:check
```

A `postToolUse` hook also checks each edited frontend file and injects formatting failures into context — fix them before moving on.
